  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the oven to 375°F (190°C).",
    "Mix together the Colby Jack cheese, spring onions, parsley, and dill in a bowl.",
    "Season with salt, black pepper, paprika, cumin, and chili flakes.",
    "In a large ceramic tagine, drizzle the olive oil and sauté the garlic until fragrant.",
    "Add the mixed cheese and herb mixture to the tagine and stir to combine.",
    "Add the lemon juice and water to the tagine and stir to mix.",
    "Cover the tagine with a lid and transfer to the preheated oven.",
    "Roast in the oven for 25 minutes, or until the cheese is melted and bubbly.",
    "Serve hot, garnished with additional parsley and dill if desired."
